            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Recovery of the blind to see."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is the age of jubilee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Amidst the famine in the world,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Rise up! To Father’s house to flee."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No recompense will be received."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No laboring in the jubilee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus! Our Jubilee!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Returned us to God and to our family."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now covered with the finest robe,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The fattened calf has slaughtered been."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This Christ our portion e’er will be."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Be merry in the jubilee!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The longing in God’s heart to be"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our portion and possession free."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Created vessels’ content be,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Fulfilled now in the jubilee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Praise God! Our Jubilee!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Rejoicing in Him, from all things we are free."
