      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When you have God, you have all things."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All things are satisfactory."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What need or deficit have we?!"
